<font color="#FF0000">NEW M-60 MEDAL STRUCK</font><br>
<tt>Tue Aug 26 14:22:50 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Silent Warrior:<br><br>
I've been hard at work... trying to come up with a M-60 medal..(I've got a tough little buddie that deserves one with &quot;C&quot; device for cosmoline!)<br><br>
I've cut the bottom out of a canteen cup with my P-38... shaped it into a small jar... etched a dead water buffalo onto it... suspended it, with ammo links,from a swath of stained camoflage underwear... two stripes... one an oily color the other brown.  I figured that the subdued colors would playdown an otherwise flashy uniform.  I laminated the whole thing with plastic to keep the flies off.<br><br>
What do you think... Silent Warrior?  Is that powerful or not?  Need some input... this is special, huh!<br><br>
Low and Slow... only way to go!  Got time to spare.. Go Army  air!<br><br>
Mustang Two Four
